All 7 datasets are merged into one input dataset by Airpoints number from monthCustomer.

input <- readRDS("data/input.RDS")
# Check NA values
plot(sapply(input, function(x) sum(is.na(x)) / length(x)) %>% sort(), ylab = 'na_perc')

2. Refactor and Imputation

  • Chatham Islands region has small counts and grouped into Hawkes Bay
  • Missing regions are imputed as Auckland
  • ADMINISTRATOR roles in AP4B are grouped as EMPLOYEE
  • Missing AP4B roles are grouped as NON_MEMBER
  • Unknown gender are grouped as Male
  • Census variables are median imputed by Region
  • Airpoints numbers are deduped in case of duplication during merge
  • All other numerics are imputed with 0
input_imp <- readRDS("data/input_imp.RDS") 
# Check NA values
plot(sapply(input_imp, function(x) sum(is.na(x)) / length(x)) %>% sort(), ylab = 'na_perc')
